title: Last Week Tonight with John Oliver  Nuclear Weapons (HBO).mkv
description:
Last Week Tonight with John Oliver: Nuclear Weapons (HBO) ___he's a comic, on HBO, with his show every night, I guess. (Don't watch TV, just videoa.)

Makes you want to go out and protest in the streets, and MAKE THE higher-ups LISTEN!

I think 90-99% of people on planet earth don't want them; the rest get hugh profits, supplying them, and planes, rockets, weapons of the military...to both sides!
